Class AdminController

java.lang.Object
com.example.lab9.controller.AdminController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/lab9/admins") @CrossOrigin(origins="http://localhost:5173") public class AdminController extends Object
REST controller for managing Admin entities and related operations. Provides endpoints for CRUD operations on admins and managing customers, employees, and orders.
